snippet.title: Visualizing Proportional Reasoning: Working With Ratios and Proportions
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com An introduction to proportional reasoning and in particular, working with ratios.  Viewers will learn what a ratio is and how we can solve for the unknown in a proportion or pair of equivalent fractions.

Examples we will look at involve visuals using the example of wins to losses for the Toronto Maple Leafs NHL Hockey Team.
